    "Finally, the widespread application of these methodologies is hampered by their limited diffusion and ease of use.",
    "De novo design requires an integrated approach combining computational science, chemistry, and biology.",
    "Many models lack this interdisciplinary aspect and are therefore computationally sophisticated but less practical from a chemical or biological standpoint.",
